  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t事情是這樣的，後知後覺昨天去晉江兔區搜錢楓强奸的新聞，然後看到朱一龍家職業粉絲在推電影預告，就點進去看了一眼，結果驚呆了，中共的文宣部門真的是不要臉哦，直接在預告裏抄襲香港反送中的口號來表現共產黨的偉大？拜托鄭州洪水把地鐵、隧道淹掉的時候，共產黨不見人的事情，真當我們是金魚嗎?<br/>\n然後又看到粉絲在吹朱一龍還朗誦過習大大的詩？立刻虎軀一震，小學生還寫過詩？立刻去翻影片看，真的有呀：“綠我涓滴，會它千頃澄碧” 大家覺得，什麽水平？<br/>\n習近平真的是照妖鏡，我今天特別想提朱一龍這個人，是因為在他演朱厚照、馮豆子、沈巍、齊衡、特別是和陳佩斯演《胡楊的夏天》的時候，我還以為他真的是清流，結果人家五體投地跪舔權貴去了，真的是驚呆了！！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9MRk1aTWd4LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/LFMZMgx.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LFMZMgx.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LFMZMgx.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9ZTGh4WXBYLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/YLhxYpX.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YLhxYpX.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YLhxYpX.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\nblob:https://imgur.com/7c03de9d-1e09-4a10-a672-09225013587a<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9heGVySjBmLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/axerJ0f.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/axerJ0f.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/axerJ0f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9vTEdwVXVELnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/oLGpUuD.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/oLGpUuD.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oLGpUuD.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS94Ukc3d05ILnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/xRG7wNH.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xRG7wNH.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xRG7wNH.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9BQXdtbmNXLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/AAwmncW.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AAwmncW.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AAwmncW.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9PTDJJMW8zLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/OL2I1o3.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OL2I1o3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OL2I1o3.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n真的做了極權的小烏龜哦<br/>\n<br/>\n哪個人說他社恐的，明明是人精！最近在批鬥流量，他居然神隱呀<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9uTWZoMkxLLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/nMfh2LK.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nMfh2LK.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nMfh2LK.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>這位美女就是他的緋聞女友，跟翟天臨一起保的研，<br/>\n其實八卦是黃曉明微博已找不到趙薇相關，都是塑料友情，初戀對象恐怕也是炒作<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96VlhuNzV1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/zVXn75u.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zVXn75u.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zVXn75u.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>老東家，據説白老闆最早做東方時空起家？真假不知，不過白岩松也姓白吼<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9MWFRIamZsLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/LXTHjfl.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LXTHjfl.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LXTHjfl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>日本旅游，有誰知道第四張照片，他斜著眼睛那張自拍背後是日本哪裏的名勝古跡嗎？奈良？東京？他也走過花美男路綫？<br/>\n最後，他的電影這麽喜歡剽竊香港反送中的口號，那走過路過不要錯過，大家一起來幫他科普一下這句話的出處咯，他是港獨分子吧，居然傳播香港廢青的口號跟標語，中影是不是跟著他一起暗戳戳造反了！<br/>\n <br/>\n接著發圖<br/>\n電影文宣裏的政府：縣長奔走疏散民衆VS 真實的中共：政府為領導視察强行通電，電倒8位救援志願者<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9XbFZ0YUtXLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/WlVtaKW.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WlVtaKW.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WlVtaKW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9RVHJHcWZULmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTrGqfT.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTrGqfT.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTrGqfT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
